1948;;The Loves of Carmen;;American;;Charles Vidor;;Rita Hayworth, Glenn Ford;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Loves_of_Carmen_(1948_film);;Following the plot of the classic opera, "Carmen," this story follows the wild gypsy's adventures as a siren and bandit. Carmen (Rita Hayworth) lures an innocent soldier (Glenn Ford) to his ruin, getting him expelled from the army. He then turns to banditry, killing Carmen's husband (Victor Jory) and others. The drama culminates in an ending with the innocent soldier repenting of his sins and dying.